// Windows resource script. Compiled by `windres` (clang/MinGW) or `rc.exe`
// (MSVC) into a .res object that ld links into the final .exe — Explorer
// then reads ICON resource id 1 to render the file's icon at every size
// it asks for (16 / 32 / 48 in the shell, 64 / 128 / 256 for thumbnails).
//
// The path is relative to this .rc file at resource-compile time, NOT to
// the working directory at link time.
1 ICON "../assets/textures/icon.ico"
